                    <biblScope unit="folio" from="4a" to="26b"/>
                    <ptr target="http://syriaca.org/manuscript/218"/>
                    <date notBefore="0818" notAfter="0888">This manuscript is written in a good current hand, of the latter part of the ixth cent. On fol. 26 a there is a note in the same handwriting, stating that this hymn-book was written, in the year 11—9. Owing to the leaf being torn, the precise date is uncertain, but the utmost limits necessarily are A. Gr. 1129, A.D. 818, and A. Gr. 1199, A.D. 888. The latter is probably very near the truth.</date>
                    <note>defective</note>
